org.globus.opensaml11.md.metadata
Interface KeyDescriptor

public interface KeyDescriptor

Corresponds to SAML Metadata Schema "KeyDescriptorType".

Provides information about the cryptographic keys that an EntityDescriptor/Provider uses to sign data. However, this is nested inside a RoleDescriptor instead of appearing at the EntityDescriptor level.

Author:
Walter Hoehn (wassa@columbia.edu)
